{
  "stem": "12051.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So did my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was so skinny that-- every time you walked into the factory, they checked you up and down whether you are not carrying out ammunition for the underground.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her ribs were sticking out to such a point we had an Ukrainian guard there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every time, he beat her that she's carrying out ammunition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Her blood was coming from her nose and from her face because he thought she's stealing ammunition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, she was starving to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because many times, I couldn't eat the soup that was made from frozen potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are jellied, black.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was sweet from those frozen potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she had that one slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She gave it to me I should be able to eat it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother never, in all the years that she was in camp, could swallow a piece of meat if you found it in the soup.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because that meat was not kosher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If meat, that was a piece of horse meat-- but if it ever found in the soup.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The funny part was that when you lined up for the soup-- the lines were very long-- we used to ask what kind of soup it is.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If it is cabbage soup, you try to run first, you know, because cabbage comes up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So you should get a little cabbage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If it's potato soup, then you went back later because you-- or bean soup, or anything-- because that goes down to the bottom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So you waited, that this watery part should be given away, that you should have anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, we were joking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were kidding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because otherwise, we couldn't have survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For example, there was one girl, we called her the Red Elsa.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
